<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1003</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ céng jīng gěi nǐ lì xià yī gè yuē, jīn shēng jīn shì bù huì ràng nǐ shī luò.
 nǐ yě céng jīng gěi zhǔ lì xià yī gè yuē, jīn shēng jīn shì yào wèi zhǔ ér huó.
 duō shǎo gè rì yè yǐ qiāo qiāo zǒu guò, shí guāng rú liú shuǐ shù yǐng pó suō.
 wú lùn nǐ zǒu dào shì jiè nǎ yī gè jiǎo luò, yé sū dōu shēn shēn qiān guà zhe.
 lái a wǒ men tóng chàng yī shǒu gǎn ēn de gē, yé sū ài nǐ yě ài wǒ.
 yǒng yuǎn jì dé zhǔ gěi wǒ men lì de yuē, cóng cǎi hóng chū xiàn de nà yī kè.
 cóng cǎi hóng chū xiàn de nà yī kè.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ zhī yuē 迦南1003</title>
</song>